Node.Notes: One of David's chief musicians. See also ps73-83.
Uncertain. Tree assumes the Mighty One, [namely] God, [namely] Yahweh.

Most see heaven and earth as merely silent witnesses of God judging. Possible heaven and earth participating (symbolically) in God's judgment, apt since they were witnesses to the enactment of their covenant relationship with God (see Deut 32:1).
